Package: MASSR
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size Re-Estimation for Two-Stage Flexible Multi-Arm Trials with Treatment Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yan Li
Maintainer: Yan Li <yanallicia23@gmail.com>
Import: MAMS
Description: This package performs sample size re-estimation (SSR) based on the conditional power approach for two-stage flexible multi-arm trial designs with normal and binary outcomes.Three flexible multi-arm designs are included in this package: flexible group sequential design (FGS), adaptive design based on inverse normal combination function (INC) and Fisher's combination function (FiC).
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
